content: I usually start my workday at 9:00 am sharp. I have two meetings scheduled, one from 1:00 pm to 2:00 pm and another from 3:00 pm to 4:00 pm. I also need to finish a report that's due by the end of the day, which I estimate will take about 2 hours to complete. I'm usually most productive during the morning hours, so I'd like to tackle the report then.
